videos.headline: Tulane scores 75-yard TD on first play of the game
videos.description: Dontrell Hilliard runs up the middle for a 75-yard touchdown on Tulane's first play of the game to take an early 7-0 lead over Army.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulane scores 75-yard TD on first play of the game) 2017/09/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulane rushes for 72-yard touchdown
videos.description: Sherman Badie rushes up the sideline for Tulane's second touchdown of over 70 yards on the day as it regains a 14-10 lead over Army.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Tulane rushes for 72-yard touchdown) 2017/09/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulane scores game winning TD
videos.description: QB Jonathan Banks fakes the handoff and runs for a 4-yard touchdown with 31-seconds left in the game, as Tulane edges out Army 21-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulane scores game winning TD) 2017/09/23 ESHEET
